{
  "text": "A related gene product, PCPE-2, shares only 43% amino acid sequence identity with PCPE-1 but has an identical domain structure [CITATION_1] and can enhance BTP procollagen C-proteinase activity [CITATION_2] .",
  "correct_citation": {
